  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of a Triptorelin 6-month Formulation in Patients With Advanced Prostate Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter, Open, Non-comparative, Phase III Study on the Efficacy, Pharmacokinetics and Safety of Two Injections of Triptorelin Embonate 22.5 mg 6-month Formulation in Patients With Advanced Prostate Cancer.</official_title>
