  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Efficacy and safety of a triptorelin 6-month formulation in patients with advanced prostate
      cancer. It was assumed that during the study treatment &gt;90% of the patients would achieve and
      maintain castrate levels of serum testosterone.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Efficacy of triptorelin treatment on gonadotropin (LH) stimulation from hypophysis, as well
      as on the PSA (prostate specific antigen) levels and safety laboratory parameters. The
      triptorelin pharmacokinetics and testosterone pharmacodynamics were assessed in a subset of
      15 patients.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
